{
  "stem": "7069.1",
  "chunk_idx": 6,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 3.0,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And when I went to his desk-- when I went to his desk-- he returned the paper to-- giving him the paper to be marked.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And I ask him, what-- what's happening?",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And he said that-- the-- I should take it back and not ask any questions.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And so therefore, soon it came out-- I found out with the other two or three Jewish kids that were in the class-- that the teachers had the order to ignore us completely, even if we sometimes-- I had sometimes an answer to a question and got up my hand.",
      "word_count": 50
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "He would completely ignore it if it was any Jewish kid.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So pretty soon we-- pretty soon, I must admit, I lost interest in school.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Even though I realized that school is there for you to learn.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But also, I think the other activities are very important.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "That's why they are there in the schools.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Right.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And there for your own well being.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So-- so I lost interest in school.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, I don't know if I would be able, at that age, to-- to evaluate that, very simply.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I could only tell, of course, it made me very unhappy when I saw the other kids went off to their-- to their soccer playing sessions.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And-- and/or the musical sessions.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "It certainly made me left out.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And I felt like I'm thrown on a--",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah, a second-class citizen.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Thrown on-- on a-- on a dung pile, practically.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And so as I say, when I eventually-- and sort of I might as well finish the school business there.",
      "word_count": 20
    }
  ],
